      <note type="important" class="- topic/note ">Always perform maintenance and preventive maintenance
according to specifications to ensure reliable operation.</note>
      <note class="- topic/note ">Always record and document the performed maintenance. This is
important to identify adjustments to the maintenance and replacement
schedules according to the specific system and environment.</note>
